  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Forward-looking troop established(constituted) by the patients having been included in the
      study &quot; PADIS EP &quot;, PHRC on 2006 and 2009, randomized checked(controlled), double-blind,
      comparing an anticoagulating treatment(processing) extended by coumadine versus placebo
      during 18 months at patients having had a first episode of EP idiopathique treated(handled)
      initially 6 months by anti-vitamin K.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
